trans-unit.source: Determines which predefined path the <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener"></xref> class uses to write its log files.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer som forhåndsdefinert bane i <xref href="Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener"> </xref> klasse bruker til å skrive loggfilene.

trans-unit.source: Assign one of the LogFileLocation enumeration values to the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Location%2A> property to specify which predefined path the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener> class uses to write its log files.
trans-unit.target: Tilordne en LogFileLocation opplisting verdiene i den <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Location%2A>til å angi som forhåndsdefinert bane i <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener>klasse bruker til å skrive loggfilene.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener> </xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.Location%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use the path for the application data that is shared among all users.
trans-unit.target: Bruk banen for programdata som deles av alle brukere.

trans-unit.source: If the string specified by <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.CustomLocation*> is not empty, then use it as the path.
trans-unit.target: Hvis strengen angitt av <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.CustomLocation*>er ikke tomt, og deretter bruke den som den banen.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Logging.FileLogTraceListener.CustomLocation*>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, use the path for a user's application data.
trans-unit.target: Ellers Bruk banen for en brukers programdata.

trans-unit.source: Use the path for the executable file that started the application.
trans-unit.target: Bruk banen for den kjørbare filen som startet programmet.

trans-unit.source: Use the path for a user's application data.
trans-unit.target: Bruk banen for en brukers programdata.

trans-unit.source: Use the path of the current system's temporary folder.
trans-unit.target: Bruk banen til den gjeldende system midlertidig mappe.
